{"tid":58197,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【我雙眼看到紅線外傳】我是要征服「絕對領域」的男人","createTime":"2016-12-28T15:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T02:29:50.000Z","uid":38966,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7b26f0dcfcdddfa760337f44ab6288cdd89f54","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"我叫阿傑，是要征服「絕對領域」的男人。<br />\n<br />\n那動人的短裙和長襪間，總有若隱若現的美腿閃現。這個長襪與短裙間魅力的神奇之處，讓人有些說不清道不明，也許正是「猶抱琵琶半遮面」，才讓人如此心動！ 它就是「絕對領域」，只用一瞬間就能將宅男「殺死」。<br />\n<br />\n所以「絕對領域」不只是短裙與襪子之間裸露的部位，而是美少女操控人心的一種武器，是一種服飾美，一種萌。<br />\n<br />\n從理性角度而言，「絕對領域」的魅力該是它統一了數學和美學，使女生的身材得以最大化地表現，所謂黃金比例正是如此。<br />\n<br />\n4:1:2.5，簡單的數字代表著不簡單的意義。4份短裙，1份大腿，2.5份膝蓋以上的長襪，這個比例使一眾宅男嚮往，即使我是一個厹，亦無法抗拒。<br />\n<br />\n如此神聖的領域，令人感到可遠觀而不可褻玩焉。<br />\n<br />\n但人和神最大的分別是神做到人做不到的事，而我要成為神，去征服這未知的領域。<br />\n<br />\n而今天是我實行的大日子，因為今天要進行校外參觀。<br />\n<br />\n原本只有我們班十多名學生外出參觀，正常而言一輛小巴足以應付。但是因為旅遊巴租車公司錯誤估算租用小巴的數目，導致我們學校沒有小巴可用。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們得到特別權利，可以使用大型旅遊巴。<br />\n<br />\n而這個人少的大型旅遊巴將會是我發動聖戰的主要場地&mdash;&mdash;征服「絕對領域」。"},{"pid":"5147ccee9058d51e0e046940d83215ef8ecba2f3","tid":58197,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0704102ea1db538e95c28cd20e7bbd5ad262fbc1","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"說了這麼久還沒說我的目標，我今天的目標是我們班一等一的美女&mdash;&mdash;紫玄茵。<br />\n<br />\n她和葉穎怡坐在旅遊巴中間靠近右邊三排座椅的位置，而我則獨自坐在後排。<br />\n<br />\n因為我們只有十四個學生，連老師在內，也只有十五個人，因此我坐在全部人的最後。<br />\n<br />\n我看見紫玄茵慢慢地坐在椅子上，長長的襪子緊包著小腿，那短裙無法完全遮蓋那白滑的肌膚。她只好任由大腿赤裸地暴露在空氣之中，一雙玉腿交疊著，那白色校裙襯托著她誘人的姿態，頗引人遐思。<br />\n<br />\n面對這人間美景，我迫不及待打算一探「絕對領域」的風光，去踏出那男生未知的世界。<br />\n<br />\n我先等旅遊巴開始移動，我望一望手上的錶，心裡默默打量。<br />\n<br />\n四十五分鐘，三排座椅的距離，足夠了。<br />\n<br />\n我先俯下身，從座椅下飽覽那醉人的風光。除了紫玄茵外，還有不少的女生。<br />\n<br />\n她們那優美渾圓的修長玉腿，嬌嫩玉潤的冰肌，雖然引人入勝，但並不是我的目標。<br />\n<br />\n我眼中只有眼前這對略透肌膚的白色長褲。<br />\n<br />\n我伏了下來，全身貼在地上，望著前方那注目的雙腿。看到並沒有其他人留意我後，我慢慢向前爬。<br />\n<br />\n一排<br />\n<br />\n兩排<br />\n<br />\n我漸漸接近那夢寐以求的雙足。心跳也隨著距離的縮短漸漸加速。"},{"pid":"81b1a42a385e1ee82eef521d3df467c996ae2f13","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打無處不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44471feb9ae4a22505c202b3f1e39a22c5739462","tid":58197,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"今日有冇正文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5899c4f30d2cfeff7d374b3e9ba4d71851416953","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日有冇正文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不了<br />\n暫停一日<br />\n因為再咁出就完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a126a67b528321a7352393421d3e202ef3a7bf","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"「噠」一聲，前面阿俊突然掉了一支筆在地上。我預想到若果他俯下身拾起那支筆，他將會發現我現在爬行的姿態。<br />\n<br />\n我的大腦如超級電腦般運行，不斷查找腦海中的解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n突然靈機一觸，右腳踏上車壁，用力蹬。身軀瞬間向逆時針方向轉了九十度。<br />\n<br />\n我若無其事地坐好，一切天衣無縫。<br />\n<br />\n結果，阿俊只是垂下手撿回筆，並沒有低頭。所有事情都沒有如我意料之中發生。<br />\n<br />\n我繼續伏地，準備下一次的前進。<br />\n<br />\n二人位    <span style=\"color: red;\">Clear</span><br />\n<br />\n三人位    <span style=\"color: red;\">Clear</span><br />\n<br />\n走廊        <span style=\"color: red;\">Clear</span><br />\n<br />\n此刻的我猶如戰場上的士兵，不能有差錯，否則一世英名將會毀於一旦。<br />\n<br />\n我還有半步就可以看到那迷人嘅「絕對領域」。<br />\n<br />\n我眼前的是一對誘人的學生鞋，而穿著它的正是紫玄茵。<br />\n<br />\n這雙白色長襪隱約顯露出柔美的曲線，裡面就是讓人聯想的纖纖玉腿。<br />\n<br />\n現在只要我轉身，我就可以看到那誘人，那令人欲罷不能的「絕對領域」。<br />\n<br />\n我的身體慢慢由伏地轉成仰天，望向發動這次聖戰的目的。"},{"pid":"5af6714c6958fa07436776b8e0e2aeea72ec7d54","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"此時此刻，我的玻璃心碎到滿地都是。<br />\n<br />\n我竟然忘記「絕對領域」在大腿之上，所以這個令人嚮往的地方，只會存在於椅子，那膝蓋以上的位置。<br />\n<br />\n我望著眼前這白花花的長襪發誓，我將會捲土重來，再一次征服你主人的「絕對領域」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為我是要征服「絕對領域」的男人</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bd3c122427a350c9876f64449ff5028d58c29f5","tid":58197,"uid":22480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"樓主考final考到痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366fa93e8f44e82f96671f7704ad27ac083f2ead","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主考final考到痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n減下壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5609fe5c546694657131558b058e7b550d940372","tid":58197,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3ad0f7d02e3655a4c3ae753965867cf433c8208c","tid":58197,"uid":1726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"69c641a7dbb345b473bb877b5139db68122fcedf","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f625947def4a5f9942684bf0e88baade3ef47815","tid":58197,"uid":70132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪傻咗"},{"pid":"4c6787676a471fb1981b8c003ee06368bc95f6e1","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係咪傻咗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c944787b4e4671e038bef3216ef163c382a01da","tid":58197,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"有冇可能會見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784c733115e0a1003aaac92ff351f582f786a502","tid":58197,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8bdfa8da8b2c8c41d28ae4acd3b5c4988d2c61fa","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇可能會見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿傑同我講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0b8fe912ca0c11d5267f6685f155befe2cd4fb","tid":58197,"uid":54663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"35375ec194b233f04ae828782c693ea3d914fcfc","tid":58197,"uid":33414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3fc0cea9f8cdd31d8e999022b439b0d136176cd8","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"「叮噹」，放學的鐘聲響起。<br />\n<br />\n我擦一擦額頭附近的汗，繼續手上的工作。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個要征服「絕對領域」的男人，我最近想到一個段子去征服它&mdash;&mdash;透過地板反光去窺探那「絕對領域」<br />\n<br />\n我在今天所有人離開課室後開始進行我的作戰計劃，因為進行地板打蠟需要一個好的天氣。<br />\n<br />\n我先用擰乾的拖把擦拭地板。確保打蠟前不要有灰塵或者其他汙物， 防止影響打蠟的光潔度，因為這關乎我的計劃成功與否。<br />\n<br />\n清潔後，我搖下裝有地板臘的容器， 並充分攪拌均勻。 然後用乾淨的抹布充分浸蘸木地板臘， 按照木地板的木紋方向仔細塗抹。<br />\n<br />\n然後就到那最重要的一步&mdash;&mdash;拋光。<br />\n<br />\n只要拋光拋得好，自然能看得更清楚。<br />\n<br />\n當我做完所有準備的時候，已經是晚上八時。我望著那簡直能當鏡子用的地板，不禁傻笑起上來。<br />\n<br />\n只要到明天，我就可以征服「絕對領域」！<br />\n<br />\n由於一整晚都在期待望著課室地板那迷人的大腿，我徹夜未眠，導致我頂著那大大的黑眼圈。<br />\n<br />\n我站在課室門外，閉上了眼。<br />\n<br />\n我心内默默地想著「只要我踏入這個門，我就可以到達烏托幫，那美麗的天堂。」<br />\n<br />\n我托起左手，慢慢把門推開。<br />\n<br />\n望著前方的景色，我提起的右腳突然僵硬，無法踏前。<br />\n<br />\n媽呀，我竟然忘記今天有體育堂，需要穿長袖運動服。<br />\n<br />\n我望向那一條條鬆身的運動褲發誓，下次我一定可以窺探它的秘密。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為我是要征服「絕對領域」的男人</span>"},{"pid":"7a3184cdde2460e9f0a02919f78aa9c78f41ed34","tid":58197,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d0e2e8924fcae36298bb2618d39aa5589422fa","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f363f920ab8ce9d0b728ba53464ea4db817136","tid":58197,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/012425_8babefe06c382c52f17dfc2d1cbbf5ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F012425_8babefe06c382c52f17dfc2d1cbbf5ad.jpg&h=0c64ce34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d97d96b11507fb6b2c54c42bca4690a9a13836b","tid":58197,"uid":38966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/012425_8babefe06c382c52f17dfc2d1cbbf5ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F012425_8babefe06c382c52f17dfc2d1cbbf5ad.jpg&h=0c64ce34&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我相信阿傑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}